dct_title_s: The official map for visitors : Oslo / published by Oslo Promotion AS.
dct_description_sm: Includes advertisements keyed to map. Within border of transit route map on verso: "Utg. 10/99--(c) Civitas/Truls Lange 1998-99." Selected buildings shown pictorially on city-center map. On verso: ancillary map "Destination Holmenkollen" and transportation ancillary map "T-bane/Trikk/Buss" in English, Norwegian, and German. Points of interest are listed and located on verso. © Cappelens forlag
